                        <span class="refund-value">{{.OriginalTransactionID}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="refund-row">
                        <span class="refund-label">Backing Date:</span>
                        <span class="refund-value">{{.OriginalTransactionDate}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="refund-row">
                        <span class="refund-label">Payment Method:</span>
                        <span class="refund-value">{{.PaymentMethod}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="refund-row">
                        <span class="refund-label">Project:</span>
                        <span class="refund-value">{{.ProjectName}}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p>Refund Amount:</p>
            <div class="amount">{{.RefundAmount}}DA</div>
        
            
            <div class="divider"></div>
            
            <p>We're sorry to see you go. If you have any feedback about your experience with the project, we'd love to hear from you.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>If you have any questions about this refund, please <a href="#" class="footer-link">contact our support team</a>.</p>
            
